comment: RHH shows that Love (CLE) makes contact with Lowry's (TOR) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Patterson (TOR) makes incidental contact with Dellavedova (CLE) that does not affect his ability to complete the pass.
DeRozan (TOR) makes incidental contact with Love (CLE) that does not affect his FOM following the screen.
Love (CLE) and Biyombo (TOR) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact with Love (CLE) that affects his RSBQ.
Valanciunas (TOR) firms up as he sets the screen on Dellavedova (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Dellavedova (CLE) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Lowry's (TOR) shot attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Lowry (TOR) was inside the three point line was confirmed.
Correctly called OOB last touched by Biyombo (TOR). Cleveland retained possession.
Dellavedova (CLE) sets the screen on Patterson (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was last touched by Biyombo (TOR) prior to going OOB was confirmed.
James (CLE) splits his feet on the perimeter at the start of his drive.
Joseph (TOR) legally contests James' (CLE) jump shot attempt.
